ğŸ§© System Architecture
Hardware Components:

ESP32 / NodeMCU (Wi-Fi microcontroller)
MQ135 Gas Sensor (Air pollutants: COâ‚‚, NHâ‚ƒ, Benzene, VOCs)
PM2.5 Sensor (Dust and fine particles)
