Firebase / ThingSpeak / InfluxDB for cloud storage
Grafana / React-based Dashboard for data visualization
TensorFlow Lite / Scikit-learn for AI prediction
MQTT or Wi-Fi protocol for data transmission
ğŸ”¬ Technical Approach
Stage	Description
Research & Requirement Analysis	Identify key parameters (COâ‚‚, PM2.5, temperature, humidity) and select low-cost sensors meeting WHO & CPCB standards.
Hardware Design	Interface ESP32 with sensors, calibrate for accuracy, and test indoor air data collection.
Software Development	Develop Arduino firmware, connect to cloud database, and create a user-friendly dashboard.
AI & Automation	Implement ML-based air quality prediction and alert mechanisms (LED/buzzer/SMS).
Integration & Testing	Deploy multiple nodes, sync data to dashboard, test stability, accuracy, and alerts.
